data.description: An inviting home in the heart of Wellington. Located within 2 miles of the Wellington Mall. This bright and airy home features a fenced in backyard, in-ground pool, split floor plan and is surrounded by an abundance of greenery. The gourmet kitchen is filled with stainless steel appliances, and granite countertops. Retreat to the primary bedroom filled with natural light, walk to the bathroom with his and her sinks, generous primary walk-in closet, secluded step in shower. Step into the dining room backing up to the French doors to the covered expansive patio. This meticulously kept home is not one that you want to miss out on viewing.
